      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm putting together some new training protocols for a group of clients and wanted to get a professional take on something. are there any actual biological differences in muscle composition or athletic potential between different racial groups that i should be factoring into my programming? just want to make sure i'm being as efficient as possible with the workouts.",
