      "content": "i get the individual variability thing, but for the sake of being data-driven, could you go into more detail on those specific fiber type differences? like, are there other specific physiological traits or genetic predispositions linked to certain ethnicities that would make them more suited for endurance vs power? i just want to see if there's a more scientific way to categorize these groups for my planning.",
